    "body": "Hello JQiue,\r\n\r\nthe preset “Nerd Font Symbols” is explicitly meant to use symbols from “Nerd Fonts”. As the name implies, it needs a “Nerd Font” to be installed and activated.\r\n\r\nThere are two other presets, that would fit your requirements:\r\n1. [No Nerd Fonts Preset](https://starship.rs/presets/no-nerd-font.html)\r\n2. [Plain Text Symbols Preset](https://starship.rs/presets/plain-text.html)\r\n\r\nTherefore, I don't consider this a bug.\r\n\r\nTake care\r\nMick\r\n\r\n\r\n",
